{"tid":1691653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人諗過咁樣用水魔法","createTime":"2019-11-03T17:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:40:32.000Z","uid":55390,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4db95b31c3465f70f6a67c35be2816945192e4ca","tid":1691653,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"利申左先 此po為家居清潔討論<br />\n見到今日咁多手足受傷好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔知點解就聯想到要做好家居清潔<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知 暫時見到最有效嘅當然係通渠水啦<br />\n我當大家驚傷及無辜好 驚技術唔好又好 始終無人可以成枝用 所以想推介另外兩樣清潔好幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 漂白水<br />\n成本極平 十零廿蚊一大支 <br />\n個個屋企都有 同埋周圍都買到 有潔癖帶出街清潔下廁所板先用有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然威力無通渠水咁好 但唔小心整親都痛掛 再唔係就算只係整到件衫都會一撻撻甩色要換<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 噴壺<br />\n都係驚整親自己整親人嘅 咪加個噴壺囉 你鍾意入漂白水又得入通渠水又得<br />\n水柱mode都有幾十cm距離 同啲胡椒乜乜咪差唔多 <br />\n操作無難度 人人都識用 好易噴到落啲窿窿罅罅<br />\n又係成本極平 搵埋俾你睇10蚊個 唔見左都唔心痛<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/Cleanic-Cleaning-Equipment-Limited/s/S1101001/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%9C%92%E8%97%9D/%E5%9C%92%E8%97%9D%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%99%B4%E6%B0%B4%E5%A3%BC-%E8%8A%B1%E7%81%91/%E6%A9%A2%E5%9C%93%E5%BD%A2%E5%99%B4%E6%B0%B4%E5%A3%BA%E5%9C%92%E8%97%9D%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%99%B4%E5%A3%BA650ML%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2/p/S1101001_S_TM-TB02W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktvmall.com%2Fhktv%2Fzh%2Fmain%2FCleanic-Cleaning-Equipment-Limited%2Fs%2FS1101001%2F%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%2582%25A2%25E4%25BF%25AC%2F%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%2582%25A2%25E4%25BF%25AC%2F%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2597%259D%2F%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2597%259D%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%2F%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A3%25BC-%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2581%2591%2F%25E6%25A9%25A2%25E5%259C%2593%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A3%25BA%25E5%259C%2592%25E8%2597%259D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%2599%25B4%25E5%25A3%25BA650ML%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2589%25B2%2Fp%2FS1101001_S_TM-TB02W&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=26951d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/Cleanic-Cleaning-Equipment-Limited/s/S1101001/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%9C%92%E8%97%9D/%E5%9C%92%E8%97%9D%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%99%B4%E6%B0%B4%E5%A3%BC-%E8%8A%B1%E7%81%91/%E6%A9%A2%E5%9C%93%E5%BD%A2%E5%99%B4%E6%B0%B4%E5%A3%BA%E5%9C%92%E8%97%9D%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%99%B4%E5%A3%BA650ML%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2/p/S1101001_S_TM-TB02W</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得有用嘅就幫手推下 希望可以幫手足搵到新技黎用<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">去清潔屋企</span> 或者見到有人跌親流血咪幫佢消下毒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b50585c4b7b4d0a45af33b3b75c940c4b71ef3","tid":1691653,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d33a8a9133d92ce2f92adce304d194fbcd392297","tid":1691653,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"甴近平1"},{"pid":"d64a3eb65a57ec771ec1417cb18f1cfa97525841","tid":1691653,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:01:33.000Z","msg":"甴近平2"},{"pid":"a6c29076a2130ab0ee8f7930ec4abe628f738f4c","tid":1691653,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:03:30.000Z","msg":"甴近平3"},{"pid":"1ca887b38e40e6d516f4ff953e1d49a678d26b98","tid":1691653,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl